Firearm's eyes narrow as he sees Choran running toward him, the Maximal not 
really paying attention to Choran's words. Without thinking, and before Rex 
could stop him, Firearm swings his arm cannon at Choran's head with full 
strengh.

Rex sighs as Firearm swings his cannon at Choran. There was no help for it, 
he thought, his friend didn't have anything resembling intelegence....
